   "source": [
    "# PFASGroups fingerprint - chain-length - branching-degree analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "Systematic study of how fingerprint configurations respond to:\n",
    "1. **Chain length** - total fluorinated carbons C2Ã¢â‚¬â€œC8\n",
    "2. **Branching degree** - linear / ÃŽÂ±-mono / ÃŽÂ²-mono / ÃŽÂ³-mono / gem-di / ÃŽÂ±+ÃŽÂ² double\n",
    "\n",
    "Compares PFASGroups configs (focused on `min_dist_to_barycenter` + `effective_graph_resistance`)\n",
    "against an overfitted PFCA discriminator (`ideal_PFCA`) - a hand-crafted upper bound\n",
    "designed to perfectly discriminate exactly this test set."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 33,
   "id": "e1337856",
   "metadata": {},
